The paper proposes a method for continual learning in neural networks, which is a topic that falls under the subfield of machine learning. Specifically, the method involves stacking parameters to retain performance on previously learned tasks, which suggests a focus on deep learning and neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CL (Computation and Language) as these sub-categories are all related to machine learning and neural networks.
